What contributes to a snow day?

Number of Previous Snow Days

  *Makes snow days less likely especially when conditions are
  not extreme. This factor effects 

Different types of snow days

  General Snow Day

  *Too much snow on the ground to be cleaned up before buses
  *Roads have too much snow to drive

    - Morning Precipitation 4am - 9am

  Ice Day/Freezing Rain

  *Heavy rainfall near 32 degrees Fahrenheit


  Delay

  *Snow projected to stop before 10-11ish
